data.description: Discover Sundance Adult Village, an inviting 55+ community in Buckeye. Nestled on a scenic golf course, it offers serene views while placed right at the neighborhood entrance. Enjoy nearby amenities like tennis courts, pools, and the Sundance Towne Center with restaurants, grocery, pharmacy, and more. Embrace a lifestyle of leisure and luxury amidst the White Tank Mountains. This spacious 2-bed + den, 2-bath home has features for comfort and convenience, such as a walk-in shower, large closets, and an open kitchen concept. There are over 20 clubs for the residents covering a variety of interests from fitness, quilting, bridge, canasta to tennis and water volleyball. The Sundance Golf Club is an 18 hole professional golf course.
